<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>MarmitaTech - Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f5f8fb;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --border: #d6e1ec;
            --primary: #0077cc;
            --primary-dark: #005fa1;
            --text: #22303f;
            --muted: #71829a;
            --shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(34, 48, 63, 0.08);
            --radius: 18px;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(180deg, #eef6fc 0%, #f9fbfd 100%);
            color: var(--text);
        }

        .page {
            width: min(1200px, 100%);
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 32px 24px 48px;
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 2.6vw, 2.6rem);
            letter-spacing: -0.03em;
        }

        .subtitle {
            color: var(--muted);
            margin-top: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: var(--radius);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            padding: 28px;
        }

        .card h3 {
            margin: 0 0 18px;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }

        form {
            display: grid;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border: 1px solid #d6e1ec;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text);
            background: #fbfdff;
            transition: border-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: rgba(0, 119, 204, 0.7);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 119, 204, 0.08);
        }

        button {
            align-self: start;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 119, 204, 0.18);
        }

        button:hover {
            background: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            display: grid;
            gap: 12px;
        }

        li {
            padding: 14px 16px;
            border-radius: 14px;
            background: #f3f7fb;
            border: 1px solid #e1e9f4;
        }

        hr {
            margin: 40px 0 24px;
            border: none;
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #d6e1ec, transparent);
        }

        .section-title {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            font-size: 1.3rem;
        }

        .note {
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--muted);
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            .page {
                padding: 20px 16px 32px;
            }

            button {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page">
        <header>
            <div>
                <h1>Painel Administrativo - MarmitaTech</h1>
                <p class="subtitle">Controle seus ingredientes, visualize itens cadastrados e gerencie o fluxo de pedidos.</p>
            </div>
        </header>

        <div class="grid">
            <div class="card">
                <h3>Novo Item (Ingrediente)</h3>
                <form action="/add-item" method="POST">
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Nome (Ex: Batata Doce)" required>
                    <input type="text" name="category" placeholder="Categoria (Ex: Carboidrato)">
                    <button type="submit">Cadastrar Item</button>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="card">
                <h3>Itens Cadastrados</h3>
                <ul>
                    <% items.forEach(item => { %>
                        <li><strong><%= item.name %></strong> <span style="color: var(--muted);">(<%= item.category %>)</span></li>
                    <% }) %>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr>
        <div class="section-title">
            <span>📦</span>
            <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.35rem;">Pedidos Ativos</h2>
        </div>
        <p class="note"><em>Aqui será implementado o Kanban nas próximas aulas...</em></p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
